#### <a name="apidoc.element.babel-core.traverse.NodePath.prototype.isCompletionRecord"></a>[function <span class="apidocSignatureSpan">babel-core.traverse.NodePath.prototype.</span>isCompletionRecord (allowInsideFunction)](#apidoc.element.babel-core.traverse.NodePath.prototype.isCompletionRecord)
- description and source-code
```javascript
function isCompletionRecord(allowInsideFunction) {
  var path = this;
  var first = true;

  do {
    var container = path.container;

    if (path.isFunction() && !first) {
      return !!allowInsideFunction;
    }

    first = false;

    if (Array.isArray(container) && path.key !== container.length - 1) {
      return false;
    }
  } while ((path = path.parentPath) && !path.isProgram());

  return true;
}
```

#### <a name="apidoc.element.babel-core.types.createTypeAnnotationBasedOnTypeof"></a>[function <span class="apidocSignatureSpan">babel-core.types.</span>createTypeAnnotationBasedOnTypeof (type)](#apidoc.element.babel-core.types.createTypeAnnotationBasedOnTypeof)
- description and source-code
```javascript
function createTypeAnnotationBasedOnTypeof(type) {
  if (type === "string") {
    return t.stringTypeAnnotation();
  } else if (type === "number") {
    return t.numberTypeAnnotation();
  } else if (type === "undefined") {
    return t.voidTypeAnnotation();
  } else if (type === "boolean") {
    return t.booleanTypeAnnotation();
  } else if (type === "function") {
    return t.genericTypeAnnotation(t.identifier("Function"));
  } else if (type === "object") {
    return t.genericTypeAnnotation(t.identifier("Object"));
  } else if (type === "symbol") {
    return t.genericTypeAnnotation(t.identifier("Symbol"));
  } else {
    throw new Error("Invalid typeof value");
  }
}
```
